---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Rapture Surfcamps"
  description="Privacy policy and data security information for Rapture Surfcamps."
  disablePopups
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 bg-dark">
    <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-20 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/30 mb-10">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
          <p>This privacy policy explains how Rapture Surfcamps ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects your personal data when you visit our website rapturecamps.com or use our services.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>
            Rapture Surfcamps<br />
            [Company legal name]<br />
            [Address]<br />
            Email: info@rapturecamps.com
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect the following types of personal data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Contact information:</strong> name, email address, phone number</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Booking data:</strong> travel dates, camp preferences, dietary requirements, surf experience level</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Payment data:</strong> processed securely through our payment provider; we do not store credit card details</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Usage data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, time spent on site</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Communication data:</strong> messages sent via contact forms, email, WhatsApp, or Telegram</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>To process and manage your booking</li>
            <li>To communicate with you about your reservation and stay</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services</li>
            <li>To send marketing communications (only with your consent)</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <p>Our website uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience and analyse site traffic. We use:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Essential cookies:</strong> required for the website to function properly</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Analytics cookies:</strong> help us understand how visitors use our site (e.g., Google Analytics)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Marketing cookies:</strong> used to deliver relevant advertisements (only with consent)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings or our cookie consent banner.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use the following third-party services that may process your data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Booking engine:</strong> for reservation processing</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Google Analytics:</strong> for website analytics</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Elfsight:</strong> for displaying customer reviews</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Zoho SalesIQ:</strong> for live chat support</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white/70">Vercel:</strong> for website hosting</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">Each of these services has their own privacy policy governing the use of your data.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law. Booking data is retained for [X] years after the completion of your stay for accounting and legal purposes.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Under applicable data protection laws (including GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
            <li>Data portability</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rapturecamps.com" class="text-ocean-light hover:underline">info@rapturecamps.com</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">9. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Our website uses SSL/TLS encryption for all data transmission.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page with the "Last updated" date above.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions or concerns about this privacy policy or your personal data, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@rapturecamps.com" class="text-ocean-light hover:underline">info@rapturecamps.com</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
